'''SM-3''' was a sentient controlled [[Droid/Legends|droid]] onboard the [[Steadfast (carrier)|''Steadfast'']] used to search destroyed vessels for traps before being salvaged.In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]] SM-3 was one of the droids involved in the finding of a operational datacore on the Star Destroyer ''[[Gnisnal]]'' that allowed for the discovery of the [[Black Fleet]].

